com.qualitestgroup.multiplan.kdt
Class TestCase

java.lang.Object
  com.qualitestgroup.multiplan.kdt.TestCase

public class TestCase
extends Object

Representation of a test case A test case is a collection of TestSteps, along with an optional DataSource. The DataSource contains argument values for test steps that have variable arguments.

Author:
Matthew Swircenski
